      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly pristine, showroom condition. This motorcar has been meticulously maintained to the highest standards, exhibiting flawless paintwork and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. With its documented service history and exceptional curb appeal, this represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. For the driver who demands nothing less than perfection, this vehicle offers unparalleled quality and long-term value.",
