    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lover! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to be parting with this absolute beauty, but it\u2019s time for her to find a new home. I\u2019ve treated this car like a member of the family\u2014always garaged, hand-washed every weekend, and kept in what I truly believe is showroom condition. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh feel inside. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been genuinely loved and cared for, you\u2019ve found it. Why don't you swing by, we can grab a coffee, and you can see for yourself how special this one is?",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
